{"tid":55504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"桂民海女疑遭內地人監視","createTime":"2016-12-26T12:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T14:23:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01ecab42b1775ac4bccfbb36acc802467ddd4c13","tid":55504,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877098&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877098%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&d=g2lStspYMc9BVbsoXhqxwwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=74a748fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877098%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&h=8609ba2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877098&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226</a><br />\n<br />\n桂民海女疑遭內地人監視<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n桂民海女兒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】銅鑼灣書店母公司股東桂民海迄今被扣押超過一年，下落未明；前店長林榮基曾在萬言書披露，桂民海今年9月至12月會被判刑，現已屆月底仍無音信。英國電訊報《The Telegraph》日前刊出桂民海女兒Angela訪問，身處英國的她表示感到緊張不安，覺得自己或被監視。<br />\n<br />\n報道中Angela指，她早前到德國法蘭克福出席書展活動，被3名操普通話的人舉機拍照，3人隨後登上一架有色車窗貨車離去。Angela估計3人來自中國大陸，「他們準確知道我甚麼時候會在那裏出現，這令我覺得有點可怕」。<br />\n<br />\nAngela說自己以電郵約朋友在展覽場地附近見面，但抵達時該3名男子直接走到她面前拍下其照片，「他們看着我，拉近相機焦距；我看了看後面，那裏甚麼都沒有，因此知道他們就是拍着我」，又透露其電郵有被自動轉發的迹象，懷疑賬戶被黑客入侵，她直言種種事件令她越來越警覺周邊環境，晚上也害怕獨自在街上行走。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基料桂已判刑林榮基昨接受《蘋果》訪問時認為，相關男子舉動未必是恐嚇Angela、要她在桂被判刑時噤聲，或許中方想將照片轉交桂民海，以證明其女兒安全，又指道理上沒必要恐嚇，因大陸不希望重提此事，「看《環時》當時社論漏夜刪文就知道，表現得方寸大亂」。林估計桂已判刑，但沒公佈也說不定。<br />\n<br />\n擁有瑞典國籍的52歲香港居民桂民海至今仍被中國扣押，Angela早前接受英國《衞報》（The Guardian）訪問時透露，瑞典警方建議她勿前往亞洲地區。今年5月，Angela到美國國會的中國委員會聽證會作證，要求美國政府向中國施壓，釋放桂民海。<br />\n<br />\n■記者馬志剛<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;歐耀佳：退休後投身人道救援<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;港區人大選舉增效忠聲明"},{"pid":"54cbf7140f993545934ae26a585e439efdd2bc60","tid":55504,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0848cd1b54b557e89a84e2ec7e2e3b6c457ac306","tid":55504,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec03350ff7fc9ac5a1a3f6c81ffddea58d61cc4b","tid":55504,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb6f5944d71deb5c1bb9e3dead1a94ae71402be","tid":55504,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國公\\國安"},{"pid":"01d7449d127429e0e9b115c7408ccb9b563c8e0f","tid":55504,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:22:51.000Z","msg":"坐洗飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7628aa01fcbc1d9a69dbf4549a37379c903bb06b","tid":55504,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"幾好，幫手燒下佢d維穩費!"}]}